{
  "texts": [
    "The criteria for triage classifications are presented below: Emergency: Call 911 or go directly to the emergency room; Non-Emergency: Try to see a doctor, but the symptoms do not require immediate attention at an emergency room.",
    "For example, you can see a doctor in the next week.",
    "Self-care: Let the health issue get better on its own and review the situation in a few days again.",
    "We tested all LLMs that we could identify through a systematic search (entering combinations of the words \"large language model\", \"LLM\", \"chatbot\", \"GPT\", \"text generation\" and \"BERT\" into search engines) and that offered a web interface.",
    "In total, we evaluated five LLMs."
  ]
}